<br>
I often have to take a day or two off EQ due to RL concerns -- like Razgum, I'm looking for a job right now and by the time I've written four cover letters and tweaked my resume four times and printed the whole mess and mailed it off, hopefully in the right envelopes, I just want to go lift weights or read the Iliad or something.<br>
<br>
Anyway, work happens -- kids happen -- computer problems happen -- and actual organic life is WAY more important than Everquest.  <br>
<br>
